Python start-up script

Original source from http://www.n8gray.org/files/pythonstartup.py

Feature

 * Shell like builtin method
  - cd, pushd, popd
  - pwd, mkdir, rmdir
  - ls, ln, cp, mv, rm
  - which (find python object type)
 * edit command which open editor to find and edit definition
 * Tab completion support
 * History support

Install

 * copy .pythonstartup*.py to your $HOME
 * add this line in $HOME/.profile file
  export PYTHONSTARTUP=$HOME/.pythonstartup.py

